description: This skill is a trivia game that asks various questions regarding Seattle, WA. Five questions are asked from a pool of random questions. See if you can get a perfect 5/5 score!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask seattle trivia to start new game
name: Seattle Trivia
shortDescription: Test your Seattle trivia. Alexa will ask you questions about Seattle, WA. See if you can get them all correct!
